name: Woof! Woof! Dogs of the Apocalypse🔥
description:
Scientists have found an animal with an amazing ability to survive in almost any environment.
These are sea sponges. According to scientists, they are not even afraid of a nuclear catastrophe or another mass extinction of all life on Earth is not terrible.
The vitality of sea sponges is surprising. They feed on particles of organics and tolerate any temperature.
In addition, they are the main "restorers" of the destroyed ecosystems of the planet, which means that they can recreate this world anew in the event of an apocalypse.
       This photo was taken using the light painting technique (Light painting is a long exposure technique with moving different light sources in front of the lens. You can also highlight objects or move the camera itself) Everything was done in real time in one shot
